":"2019-11-25T23:18:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"faea55f263143207e09a3c39640b2f4ffac7535e","tid":1755517,"uid":199553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T23:20:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f78e91e4343b251e514784851b8ad140f4ca6648","tid":1755517,"uid":32675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T23:28:44.000Z","msg":"立子總係睇得透<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b02ad2d3dab184aed5d33ac26af0f37ea04ba56e","tid":1755517,"uid":33437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T23:29:02.000Z","msg":"puah"},{"pid":"5c5dc70a4b9d5b049bfd1d828fae43bf32d4a3b5","tid":1755517,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T23:43:46.000Z","msg":"呢個都係點解市政局應該重建嘅原因之一<br />\n改咗做區議會之後，區議會根本就係愛嚟畀班仆街掠水嘅利益資源集團<br />\n犯民都算，佢哋都叫做有資源做區，蛇齋餅糭可以照派<br />\n兒登細路未必知，蛇齋餅糭本身都係犯民發明<br />\n素人要真係做到區，始終都係要有資源"},{"pid":"ff03c49f0d1206983366b28a22d795dda756f310","tid":1755517,"uid":48868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T23:45:22.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"17f485d38a5c5f47cf1eec66c9c3a57621007ed7","tid":1755517,"uid":67277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T23:59:00.000Z","msg":"議員要做好地區工作，選民都要做好監督既工作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係投完就算"},{"pid":"7bce70f9ebb4fec6a81e8dffb4b1de179c5aa270","tid":1755517,"uid":31952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T00:06:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a552f73558d01201be69d8a2a762ae434c45051b","tid":1755517,"uid":220942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T00:07:07.000Z","msg":"一定狂搵黑材料"},{"pid":"4595216fa74fef37c7fa633bd7163d0e2ebd0b1b","tid":1755517,"uid":31952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T00:07:38.000Z","msg":"正經文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj